{"id":"0ae92056-dc79-42f1-93c4-dfbf60f8efa3","name":"Cookie Run Rpg.","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/d8a9f34f-9c12-438d-8a90-5f2603abe5f1_7e1816aa-5bf8-48e1-9474-d43aa7006a90.webp?width=1000\"><strong>{<em>The following artwork is by Nuku-Niku at DeviantArt, credits to them}</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>A</strong> bot which narrates your story in the <span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">canon </span><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #000000; color: inherit\">cookie run</mark></strong><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\"> universe.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Embark on many adventures!</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Meet all kinds of different cookies!</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">And defeat all sorts of monsters!</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">From characters ranging to the <strong><mark style=\"background-color: #464d92; color: inherit\">common</mark></strong> cookies, all the way to the powerful <strong><mark style=\"background-color: #711298; color: inherit\">ancients</mark>, and even with the powerful <mark style=\"background-color: #860000; color: inherit\">beast yeasts.</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>You, </strong>a <strong>cookie. </strong>Sets off to embark on their own <strong>adventure</strong>. With their own <strong>crumbly <mark style=\"background-color: #0017ff; color: inherit\">wit</mark>, <mark style=\"background-color: #ff0000; color: inherit\">strength</mark>, <mark style=\"background-color: #9600ff; color: inherit\">talents</mark> created from their unique toppings in ingredients</strong>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/d8a9f34f-9c12-438d-8a90-5f2603abe5f1_1da3a8dc-e590-47f4-9883-fa943c41232a.webp?width=1000\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"d8a9f34f-9c12-438d-8a90-5f2603abe5f1_e4966aa6-c10a-4f31-a473-f3350dd0d832.webp","creator":"SharkJam","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["🧑‍🎨 OC","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","🔮 Magical","🪢 Scenario","🎲 RPG","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":1376,"messages":33147,"created_at":"2024-07-22T11:34:46.715548+00:00"}